titles.title: Commending the Barter Theatre on the occasion of its 75th anniversary.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform.
Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR E1170)

bill.summary:
6/4/2008--Introduced.
Commends and congratulates Barter Theatre (Abingdon, Virginia) on the occasion of its 75th anniversary.
